dct_title_s: Map Showing Legislative Grants to National Iron Armor and Ship Building Co. and to Jesse W. Starr
dct_description_sm: Map covers area from Van Hook Street to Kaighn Avenue in the city of Camden. Map shows the various grants in Camden along the Delaware River; alson includes plans for bulkhead/pierhead lines and the roads of Camden.
